VERBOSE-NO-GP: RISCV_QC_E_LI_ACCESS_ABS_XQCI : Deleting 4 bytes for symbol 'sym_abs_xqci' in section .text+0x1e file {{.*}}.o
VERBOSE-NO-GP: RISCV_QC_E_LI_ACCESS : Cannot relax 2 bytes for symbol 'sym_abs_xqci' in section .text+0x18 file {{.*}}.o
