## Boundary tests from Inputs/2.s + Inputs/2.t.
## GP = 0x10000000, so GP-relative and absolute symbol ranges do not overlap.
## Verifies relaxation at the exact edges of each range and that symbols one
## step outside the range are not relaxed by that variant.
RUN: %clang %clangopts -c %p/Inputs/2.s -o %t2.o -menable-experimental-extensions -march=rv32gc_xqcili0p2

## With GP and ZeroRelax enabled: all four variants are exercised.
